eant that the ROC cannot act as a national Olympic committee or receive financing from the Olympic movement.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2431, \"end\": 2434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999866802228, \"rank\": 1.331983371253686e-08, \"text\": \"ROC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC however reserved the right to clear Russian athletes to take part in the Olympic Games in Paris in 2024 as neutrals.\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2530, \"end\": 2533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4914312070236156e-30, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2570, \"end\": 2577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.7391333790113638, \"rank\": 0.3112416108032897, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999975628536644, \"rank\": 2.4371522014816626e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later, IOC President Thomas Bach said that Russian athletes should have no affiliation with the ROC if they want to compete at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2658, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IOC President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 2694, \"end\": 2701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.7391333790113638, \"rank\": 0.3112416108032897, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 2747, \"end\": 2750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999866802228, \"rank\": 1.331983371253686e-08, \"text\": \"ROC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}]}"